#: index.docbook:923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you playback two streams or more in one session and you are watching the "
"previous one, <action>will select the next one</action>."
msgstr ""
"यदि भवान् एकस्मिन् सत्रे द्वौ प्रवाहौ वा अधिकं वा प्लेबैक् करोति तथा च पूर्ववर्तीं पश्यति "
