"and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-restore.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icons. <action>Switch the "
"full screen mode</action>."
msgstr ""
"तथा <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-restore.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> चिह्नानि । <action>पूर्णपर्दे "
"मोड् परिवर्तयन्तु</action> ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:941
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Minimal Mode/Exit Minimal "
"Mode</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>.</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>प्लेबैक</guimenu> <guimenuitem>न्यूनतमविधिः/न्यूनतममोडतः निर्गच्छ</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"and <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-fullscreen.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> icons. <action>Switch "
"the minimal mode</action>. A &GUI; mode in a window, where we only have "
"contextual menu and keyboard shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"तथा <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"view-fullscreen.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject> चिह्नानि । "
"<action>न्यूनतमं मोडं परिवर्तयन्तु</action> । A &GUI; mode इति विण्डो मध्ये, यत्र अस्माकं "
"केवलं contextual menu तथा keyboard shortcuts सन्ति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:954
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Subtitle</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>प्लेबैक</guimenu> <guimenuitem>उपशीर्षक</guimenuitem>"

