"Offers a drop-down list with <action>options related to the audio stream(s)</"
"action>."
msgstr "श्रव्यप्रवाह(s)</action>सम्बद्धैः <action>विकल्पैः सह ड्रॉप्-डाउन-सूचीं प्रदाति ।"

