"<action>Offers a drop-down list with available aspect ratios</action>, more "
"an <guimenuitem>Automatic</guimenuitem> option. The <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Aspect_ratio_(image)\">aspect ratio of an image</ulink> "
"describes the proportional relationship between its width and height."
msgstr ""
"<action>उपलब्धपक्ष-अनुपातैः सह एकं ड्रॉप्-डाउन-सूचीं प्रदाति</action>, अधिकं "
"<guimenuitem>स्वचालित</guimenuitem> विकल्पः । चित्रस्य <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Aspect_ratio_(image)\">आस्पेक्ट् रेश्यो</ulink> तस्य विस्तारस्य "
"ऊर्ध्वतायाः च आनुपातिकसम्बन्धं वर्णयति ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1087
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Video</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Video size</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>प्लेबैक</guimenu> <guisubmenu>वीडियो</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>वीडियो "
"आकारः</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1092
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a drop-down list with available video sizes</action>. Change "
"the size of the image by a percentage, more <guimenuitem>Automatic</"
"guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Original Size</guimenuitem> options."
msgstr ""
"<action>उपलब्ध-वीडियो-आकारैः सह एकं ड्रॉप्-डाउन-सूचीं प्रदाति</action> । प्रतिबिम्बस्य "
"आकारं प्रतिशतेन परिवर्तयन्तु, अधिकानि <guimenuitem>स्वचालित</guimenuitem> तथा "
"<guimenuitem>मूल आकारः</guimenuitem> विकल्पाः ।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Jump to Position</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>J</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>प्लेबैक</guimenu> <guimenuitem>स्थानं प्रति कूदन्तु</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a spin box for setting the desired time point to which you "
"want to go</action>; with hours, minutes and seconds."
msgstr ""
"<action>इष्टसमयबिन्दुं सेट् कर्तुं स्पिनबॉक्सं प्रदाति यस्मिन् भवान् गन्तुम् इच्छति</action>; "
"घण्टाभिः, निमेषैः, सेकेण्ड्भिः च सह।"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Skip</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>प्लेबैक</guimenu> <guimenuitem>अतिक्रम्य</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Offers a drop-down list with four predefined jump times</action>. "
"With the following options:"
msgstr ""
"<action>चतुर्भिः पूर्वनिर्धारितैः कूर्दनसमयैः सह एकं पतनसूचीं प्रदाति</action> । "
"निम्नलिखितविकल्पैः सह :"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: index.docbook:1126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Shift;&Left;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Playback</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skip</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Skip "
